author: Nintendo of America
description:
Experience the ultimate galactic adventure in Star Wars Outlaws Gold Edition, out now on Nintendo Switch 2: https://ninten.do/6050seqaE 
  
Take on high-risk, high-reward missions from the galaxy’s crime syndicates. Steal valuable goods, infiltrate secret locations, and outwit enemies as one of the galaxy’s most wanted. Every choice you make influences your ever-changing reputation. If you’re willing to take the risk, the galaxy is in your hands. 
 
 
#NintendoSwitch2 #StarWarsOutlaws
title: Star Wars Outlaws Gold Edition – Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch 2

author: Nintendo of America
description:
Hollow Knight: Silksong is out now on Nintendo Switch 2 and Nintendo Switch! Play now: https://ninten.do/6055s5D6S 

Experience the epic sequel to the award winning action-adventure, Hollow Knight! Play as the lethal hunter, Hornet, who is captured and taken to an unfamiliar world. Explore mossy grottos, gilded cities, and misted moors to ascend to the peak of this beautifully handcrafted haunted world. Craft weapons and learn new abilities to engage in lethal acrobatic combat to vanquish hordes of bugs, beasts, and legendary bosses. Help Hornet restore hope to a fallen kingdom. 
 
#HollowKnight #Silksong #NintendoSwitch2 #NintendoSwitch
title: Hollow Knight: Silksong – Nintendo Switch 2 Edition – Launch Trailer
